OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,FA former Scout leader who force-fed
OL,7,Fspicy food to a child has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to 18 months in prison.
OL,10,FBeverley Rose Colley, 56, was
OL,11,Fsentenced at Jersey's Royal Court
OL,12,Ftoday (Thursday 28 May) for four
OL,13,Foffences, including common assaults
OL,14,Fand intentionally causing harm to a
OL,15,Fchild.
OL,17,FShe was found guilty of the crimes
OL,18,Fafter a five-day trial in March.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
