PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,FDeputy Bailiff Mark Temple, who
OL,7,Fpresided over the case, said the
OL,8,Fvictim "sustained a campaign of abuse
OL,9,Ffor which (Colley) showed no remorse".
OL,11,FDeputy Bailiff Temple also handed
OL,12,FColley a restraining order to protect
OL,13,Fthe victim.
OL,15,FThe Royal Court heard that Colley
OL,16,Fforce-fed the child hot chilli sauce,
OL,17,Fhit them with the flat edge of a bread
OL,18,Fknife and a wooden spoon, and threw a
OL,19,Fhot meal at them.
OL,26,@qD@KpmqD@Rpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
