OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,FThe Court also heard that Colley was
OL,7,Falso known to verbally abuse the child
OL,8,Fwith name-calling.
OL,10,FCrown Advocate Mike Preston, for the
OL,11,Fprosecution, told the court that
OL,12,FColley's offences were "brazen and
OL,13,Fcruel" and that her actions
OL,14,Fdemonstrated a "deliberate disregard
OL,15,Ffor the welfare" of the child.
OL,17,FAdvocate Preston also said that
OL,18,FColley's victim suffered "serious
OL,19,Fpsychological and developmental harms"
OL,20,Fand felt "emotional isolation" as a
OL,21,Fresult of the abuse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,FCrown Advocate James Bell, for the
OL,7,Fdefence, said that Colley understood
OL,8,Fthe gravity of the situation, and
OL,9,F"regrets that (her victim) feels this
OL,10,Fway".
OL,12,FStates of Jersey Police welcomed the
OL,13,Fverdict. In a statement, they said the
OL,14,Fverdict "re-enforces that violence and
OL,15,Fabuse, especially against those who
OL,16,Fare vulnerable by way of their age, is
OL,17,Fnot and should not be tolerated."
OL,26,@qD@OpmqD@Zpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
