OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,F"These historical offences caused
OL,7,Fserious and lasting harm to the victim
OL,8,Fand the impact continues to be felt
OL,9,Ftoday," the statement reads.
OL,11,F"We commend the victim's courage in
OL,12,Fcoming forward, supporting a police
OL,13,Finvestigation and ultimately seeing
OL,14,Fthe case through to a Royal Court
OL,15,Ftrial.
OL,17,FColley, who served in the two most
OL,18,Fsenior Scout positions in Jersey, is
OL,19,Fnow banned from the organisation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
