OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780146665
OL,3,CFormer Scout leader who force-fed
OL,4,Cchild spicy food jailed for 18 months
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Scout Association
OL,7,Fsaid: "Keeping young people safe is
OL,8,Four top priority.
OL,10,F"These offences took place outside of
OL,11,FScouting. Colley was suspended from
OL,12,FScouts in April 2024, and her
OL,13,Fmembership has since been cancelled.
OL,15,F"We carry out rigorous vetting of all
OL,16,Fadults who work with young people and
OL,17,Frequire them to follow a strict code
OL,18,Fof conduct."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
